reference/workflows.title: Workflows
reference/workflows.description: This document describes where Schematic fits in data and analytics projects and the end-to-end situations it supports. Schematic is built for individual data projects: one repo = one schema project, with one or more environments (dev, test, prod). It focuses on the schema layer—defining and versioning catalogs, schemas, tables, and governance—within the broader data ops flow.
